title: Emilia Clarke Sings R. Kelly at Her Game of Thrones Wrap Party for 1
text:
by: Olivia Bahou 
Season 7 of Game of Thrones is this much closer to hitting our TV screens. How can we be sure? Khaleesi told us so. 
Emilia Clarke shared a video to Instagram on Friday of her mini "wrap party" for one, and she's clearly excited about what she just filmed. Wearing the platinum blonde wig that she dons as the Mother of Dragons, Clarke lip syncs to R. Kelly's "I Believe I Can Fly," and even she can't keep a straight face. 
VIDEO: Emilia Clarke's Beauty Transformation 

"That feeling when at last you're a day away from wrapping season 7," she wrote . "I BELIEVE THIS ONES GONNA BE A MIND BLOWERâ€¦ #itakemyjobseriouslyiSWEAR." A video posted by @emilia_clarke on Feb 3, 2017 at 5:49am PST 
Will Daenerys Targaryen take the Iron Throne? Unite with her long lost nephew Jon Snow? Find a husband in Westeros? We'll have to wait until Season 7 premieres this summer to find out.
